{"tid":1087714,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"20巴 處 到底應唔應該繼續守住個處？","createTime":"2019-04-01T13:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T14:37:04.000Z","uid":238361,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e6771a517e4d6db6dc4c3b5ef940e3f6079fb6","tid":1087714,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"第時我一定會搵處女做我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我亦都要將自己最好嘅處留俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果女神而家撩我扑嘢，我去唔去馬好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我女神一定係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我好可能係扑緊自己未來老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但萬一女神唔係我將來嘅老婆呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我將來嘅處女老婆一定好hurt<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路洞房一路諗我都對過其他女仔做過一樣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟，我應唔應該繼續守住個處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcadaccce83d8a22aaf2e913644393b234cf329","tid":1087714,"uid":230890,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3553bac0909d9199bca79bf321fd6edf4bc6d9ee","tid":1087714,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"準備留過世啦"},{"pid":"8d7f70a28c510d1d77d0411428bb88284f9cb9ef","tid":1087714,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"緊係死守，再戒丁儲起D精。"},{"pid":"5289ef910a57cf02b011028674784cc276223ef2","tid":1087714,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3553bac0909d9199bca79bf321fd6edf4bc6d9ee","tid":1087714,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"準備留過世啦"},"cite